  coach_language = 'Primary subrole: acceleration_start_speed. Coach Split-Stance Auditory Sprint Start as a quality-first reaction drill: define the cue, remove ambiguous starts, require a clean answer, and rest long enough that speed, accuracy, posture, and safety stay intact.',
