  card_summary = 'Closeout-to-Catch-Redirect is a reaction-time-reduction drill for closeout reaction plus catch and second decision. Use it when the goal is faster stimulus recognition, cleaner first movement, and safer reset behavior without turning reaction work into conditioning.',
