  coaching_execution = '{"movement_description":"Closeout-to-Catch-Redirect: the athlete responds to partner pass plus redirect call with the required answer: closeout, catch, redirect, and reset.","setup":["Create a clear start position and target area.","Define the valid cue and any decoy cues.","Use enough spacing that a wrong response does not create collision risk.","Give one low-speed rehearsal before randomized reps."],"execution_steps":["Athlete sets posture and waits without pre-loading into the answer.","Coach or partner gives the cue at an unpredictable time.","Athlete reacts only to the valid cue and completes the movement response.","Athlete brakes, catches, or finishes safely.","Athlete resets breathing, stance, and attention before the next cue."],"breathing_cues":["Breathe quietly before the cue.","Exhale during the reset, not during the wait as a false trigger.","Avoid breath-holding across repeated cues."],"coach_cues":["Wait for information.","First step answers the cue.","Fast eyes, quiet body.","Brake before the next rep.","Reset so the next rep is real."],"athlete_cues":["Do not guess.","See it, then go.","Clean finish.","Reset your eyes and feet."],"quality_gate":["At least 80-90% correct responses at the chosen speed before progression.","No unsafe collisions, stumbles, or uncontrolled finishes.","Response quality stays crisp across the set."],"common_faults":["jumping early before the cue","turning the drill into a race or conditioning station","adding too many cue choices too soon","late braking or unsafe spacing","looking at the coach instead of the relevant target when scanning is required"],"stop_signs":["false starts or wrong choices stack up","athlete cannot explain the cue rule","mechanics degrade from fatigue","pain or symptoms appear"]}'::jsonb,
